reviewText: Lovely Jane Russell is at her sassy best.  She sings some very wonderful songs.  She brings smiles & laughter to her viewers.  Romance and misunderstanding abound.  It's great fun to watch.  You might even catch yourself singing along with Jane!  Sure wish it were available on DVD!
